### âœ… Channel Status & Monitoring

DISPLAY CHSTATUS(*)
DISPLAY CHSTATUS(<CHANNEL_NAME>)
DISPLAY CHSTATUS(<CHANNEL_NAME>) ALL


### âœ… Channel Definition Check

DISPLAY CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) ALL
DISPLAY CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) CONNAME


### âœ… Start / Stop Channels

START CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>)
STOP CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) STATUS(INACTIVE)
STOP CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) STATUS(STOPPED)
STOP CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) MODE(FORCE)


### âœ… Reset Channel Seq Numbers

RESET CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) SEQNUM(1)


### âœ… SSL / TLS Channel Checks

DISPLAY CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) SSLCIPH
DISPLAY CHSTATUS(<CHANNEL_NAME>) SSLPEER
DISPLAY QMGR SSLKEYR
REFRESH SECURITY TYPE(SSL)


### âœ… CHLAUTH Debugging

DISPLAY CHLAUTH(*)
DISPLAY CHLAUTH(<CHANNEL_NAME>) ALL
DISPLAY CHSTATUS(<CHANNEL_NAME>) MCAUSER
ALTER QMGR CHLAUTH(DISABLED)   # Only for testing!


### âœ… Network & Connectivity Troubleshooting

ping <remote_host>
telnet <remote_host> <port>

Check MQ listener:

DISPLAY LSSTATUS(<LISTENER>) ALL
STOP LISTENER(<LISTENER>)
START LISTENER(<LISTENER>)


### âœ… Logs & Queue Depth

tail -f /var/mqm/errors/AMQERR01.LOG
tail -f /var/mqm/qmgrs/<QMGR>/errors/AMQERR01.LOG
DISPLAY QLOCAL(SYSTEM.DEAD.LETTER.QUEUE) CURDEPTH


### âœ… Retry / Bounce Control

ALTER CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) SHORTTMR(60)
ALTER CHANNEL(<CHANNEL_NAME>) LONGRTY(999999)

